241
00:33:20,880 --> 00:33:21,840
CHAPTER NINE

242
00:33:22,720 --> 00:33:24,800
Help from Carmine Noccia

243
00:33:27,040 --> 00:33:31,840
On Tuesday afternoon, Jack 
was in his office with Emilio.  

244
00:33:32,960 --> 00:33:39,440
