246
00:33:49,360 --> 00:33:59,520
There was no DNA, no gun, nothing. We need 
to talk to Carmine Noccia in Las Vegas."

247
00:34:01,680 --> 00:34:09,200
Carmine and his family knew every professional 
killer from California to Florida.  

248
00:34:10,800 --> 00:34:20,720
Jack didn't often work with men like Carmine. 
But, once, Carmine asked for Private's help -  

249
00:34:20,720 --> 00:34:30,560
his daughter ran away, and he wanted her back. 
