250
00:34:32,240 --> 00:34:35,760
"We'll fly to Las Vegas," Jack said.

251
00:34:37,600 --> 00:34:45,120
Carmine was very rich, and his home was 
in a park, half an hour from the airport.  

252
00:34:46,400 --> 00:34:53,360
Two big men came to meet Jack and Emilio 
at the door and took their guns from them.

253
00:34:55,520 --> 00:34:57,920
Carmine was in the sitting room.

254
00:34:59,360 --> 00:35:03,200
"Good to see you, Jack," said Carmine.

255
00:35:04,560 --> 00:35:07,360
"I need your help," said Jack.

256
00:35:08,560 --> 00:35:19,120
"Jack, you helped me, and I'll help 
you. But don't ask again," said Carmine.

257
00:35:21,440 --> 00:35:27,680
"Someone killed my friend Shelby 
Cushman in Los Angeles - a professional.  

258
00:35:28,800 --> 00:35:33,280
Who was the killer, do you know?" said Jack.

259
00:35:34,960 --> 00:35:43,840
"I don't know. But I can ask. I'll 
call you when I know," said Carmine.

260
00:35:46,000 --> 00:35:54,880
The call from Carmine came late at night. 
