261
00:35:57,040 --> 00:36:05,040
Jack called Emilio early Wednesday 
morning. Emilio said he knew Bo Montgomery.  

262
00:36:06,400 --> 00:36:12,880
Bo was a professional killer, and he 
lived on a horse farm in the Agoura Hills.

263
00:36:14,560 --> 00:36:20,720
Jack and Emilio drove there fast. 
They stopped near the farmhouse.

264
00:36:22,240 --> 00:36:33,920
A door opened slowly, and a man came out. He 
had a big dog, and in his arms was an AK-47.  

265
00:36:35,680 --> 00:36:39,920
"What do you want?" he asked.

266
00:36:39,920 --> 00:36:46,080
"I'm Jack Morgan, from Private. 
I'm working for Andy Cushman.  

267
00:36:47,120 --> 00:36:54,160
Someone killed his wife, 
Shelby. Who paid for that?"

268
00:36:54,160 --> 00:36:59,360
Bo Montgomery thought for a 
minute and then spoke slowly.  

269
00:37:00,800 --> 00:37:08,960
"I don't know Shelby Cushman. I 
don't know any women in Bluffs."

270
00:37:10,720 --> 00:37:19,200
Then, he wrote a name on the ground with 
the end of his gun. Jack looked at the name,  

271
00:37:20,160 --> 00:37:22,240
