273
00:37:37,200 --> 00:37:38,160
CHAPTER TEN

274
00:37:39,120 --> 00:37:39,840
DNA

275
00:37:42,160 --> 00:37:49,840
Christine Castiglia wanted to meet 
Justine again, on Wednesday after school.

276
00:37:50,560 --> 00:37:54,480
"Let's go to the coffee shop on Melrose Avenue,"  

277
00:37:55,440 --> 00:38:01,440
said Christine. "I'll remember better 
there about the boys and the van."

278
00:38:02,800 --> 00:38:05,040
"Great," said Justine.

279
00:38:06,800 --> 00:38:10,640
The coffee shop was the same as five years before.  

280
00:38:12,160 --> 00:38:19,280
"My mum and I sat here," said Christine. 
