293
00:39:56,800 --> 00:40:07,120
but we don't know them. But I talked to Christine 
Castiglia. We looked at some photos, and she saw  

294
00:40:07,120 --> 00:40:18,240
this boy. He pushed Wendy Borman into the van. 
