296
00:40:29,680 --> 00:40:36,240
"Maybe this is Steemcleena. And 
you want his DNA?" said Nora.

297
00:40:37,360 --> 00:40:41,680
"Yes. Can you help me?" said Justine.

298
00:40:44,720 --> 00:40:52,480
Nora and Justine stopped their car near Crocker's 
