301
00:41:16,160 --> 00:41:19,840
The two women went into the bar after him.

302
00:41:20,880 --> 00:41:27,040
There were a lot of people in the 
bar. Crocker was in the corner with  

303
00:41:27,040 --> 00:41:33,840
a man with long hair. Justine bought 
drinks, and the two women watched.

304
00:41:35,520 --> 00:41:42,800
Half an hour later, the men finished 
their drinks and left. Nora and Justine  

305
00:41:43,440 --> 00:41:47,840
quickly went to the men's 
table and took the glasses.

306
00:41:49,120 --> 00:41:52,000
In the car, Justine called Sci.  

307
00:41:53,440 --> 00:42:01,840
"Can you meet us at Private in twenty minutes?" 
