310
00:42:21,680 --> 00:42:30,560
"Jack, why are you here now? It's 
1 a.m. You look tired!" said Andy.

311
00:42:31,920 --> 00:42:38,720
"I am tired," said Jack. "Today, 
I drove to the Agoura Hills.  

312
00:42:40,080 --> 00:42:45,360
How much did you pay Bo 
Montgomery to kill Shelby?"

313
00:42:47,120 --> 00:42:53,120
Andy started to cry. "You don't understand, Jack,"  

314
00:42:54,160 --> 00:43:04,000
