329
00:45:00,240 --> 00:45:04,320
"Where is Morbid?" asked Jack.

330
00:45:04,320 --> 00:45:07,360
"I don't know," said Mo-bot.

331
00:45:10,320 --> 00:45:16,000
Justine and Nora drove to Crocker's 
office on Wilshire Boulevard.

332
00:45:17,680 --> 00:45:22,960
"Mr. Crocker is on vacation 
today," said the woman at the desk.

333
00:45:24,720 --> 00:45:28,880
