341
00:46:20,400 --> 00:46:25,760
Jack and Emilio were on the 
road, too. Mo-bot called Jack.

342
00:46:27,520 --> 00:46:31,280
"I'm reading more messages 
from Morbid to Graciella,"  

343
00:46:32,000 --> 00:46:39,280
