362
00:49:03,520 --> 00:49:05,440
The police took Crocker away.  

363
00:49:06,720 --> 00:49:15,840
Justine looked at Nora. "We need to go to his 
apartment and look for Wendy Borman's necklace."

364
00:49:16,800 --> 00:49:26,160
Justine and Nora looked everywhere in Crocker's 
apartment. They found nothing. Justine opened  

365
00:49:26,160 --> 00:49:35,120
