clothes again. The light was on a string, and she  

366
00:49:35,120 --> 00:49:45,360
pulled it. She looked at the end of the string in 
her hand. It was the star from Wendy's necklace.

367
00:49:48,640 --> 00:49:56,640
"We've caught them, Justine," said Jack, 
back at Private. "Sci looked at the DNA  

368
00:49:56,640 --> 00:50:02,720
from Crocker's blood. It's the same 
as the DNA from Wendy's clothes."

369
00:50:05,120 --> 00:50:08,880
The next morning, Jack's phone woke him early.  

370
00:50:10,560 --> 00:50:21,520
"Jack, it's Carmine Noccia. I have some bad 
news for you. Your friend Andy Cushman is dead.  

371
00:50:22,880 --> 00:50:28,800
His car went off the road near 
Marin, and it went into the ocean."

372
00:50:30,800 --> 00:50:35,840
"Did anybody see Andy's car 
go into the ocean?" said Jack.

373
00:50:37,040 --> 00:50:49,520
"Oh, yes. One of my cousins saw it. He was the 
only person there. Have a good day," said Carmine.

374
00:50:51,360 --> 00:51:00,720
Jack looked at his phone for a minute and 
thought, "Carmine's cousin killed Andy." Then,  

375
00:51:01,520 --> 00:51:13,440
